  "texts": [
    "Emission filters were 445/46 (for DAPI), 521/38 (for Alexa Fluor 488), and 594/43 (for Alexa Fluor 555).",
    "Images were deconvolved in Fusion/Autoquant (version XYZ) using XYZ settings.",
    "For live cell imaging, U373 cells were plated into 4-well glass bottom chamber slides (5 × 10 4 cells/well).",
    "TMZ (20 µM) was diluted in culture media and directly added to wells.",
    "Adenovirus (AdGFP-Polκ or AdYFP-Pol) was added into culture media 24 hours before imaging."
